 《血钻石》和《角斗士》明星杰曼·翰苏尽管事业辉煌，但“努力谋生” https://www.nme.com/news/film/djimon-hounsou-struggling-to-make-a-living-3828340?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=djimon-hounsou-struggling-to-make-a-livingVictoria Luxford Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:11:32 +0000 Film NewsNewsEmmysGolden GlobesOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3828340 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰曼·翰苏" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我仍然在经济上陷入困境。我的工资肯定过低”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/djimon-hounsou-struggling-to-make-a-living-3828340">《血钻》和《角斗士》的主演杰蒙·翰苏 (Djimon Hounsou) 尽管有着辉煌的职业生涯，但“努力谋生”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰曼·翰苏" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/guardians-of-the-galaxy"><em>《银河护卫队》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2"><em>《角斗士》</em></a>的主演杰曼·翰苏透露，尽管他在电影业取得了数十年的成功，但由于系统性种族主义，他仍然在经济上陷入困境。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/quiet-place-day-1-review-lupita-nyongo-3768910">《安静的地方：第一天》评论：回归基础的前传感觉更小，但仍然值得尖叫</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位贝宁演员在史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格 1998 年的历史剧<em>《Amistad》</em>中取得了突破，此后他一直在努力工作，出演了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/rebel-moon">《叛逆的月亮》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/shazam">《雷霆沙赞》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/a-quiet-place-day-one"><em>《寂静之地：第一天</em></a>》等影片。他曾凭借<em>《Amistad》</em>和 2006 年与莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥合作的惊悚片<em>《血钻》</em>获得两项<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡金像奖</a>提名。</p><p>他在<a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2025/01/11/world/video/actor-djimon-hounsou-sparks-pan-african-unity-through-nonprofit"><em>美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 的非洲之声变革者</em></a>节目中谈到，业界尚未为他的工作支付足够的报酬。 “我仍在为谋生而奋斗，”他说。 “我从事电影制作行业已有二十多年了，获得了两项奥斯卡提名和许多大片，但我仍然在经济上陷入困境。我的工资肯定偏低”。</p><p>翰苏认为，系统性种族主义是问题的根源，并声称业界对他的态度可以追溯到他与<em>Amistad 的</em>颁奖活动。 “我获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/golden-globes">金球奖</a>提名，但奥斯卡奖他们却忽略了我，因为他们认为我刚刚从船上和街头走下来，”他回忆道。 “尽管我成功地做到了这一点，但他们就是不觉得我是一个值得他们尊重的演员”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3828348" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828348" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828348" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Gladiator.jpg" alt="杰曼·翰苏" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Gladiator.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Gladiator-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Gladiator-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Gladiator-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Gladiator-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Djimon-Hounsou-Gladiator-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828348" class="wp-caption-text">杰蒙·翰苏（中）与《角斗士》的演员和工作人员在一起（图片来源：LUCY NICHOLSON/AFP via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>主持人拉里·马多沃对此表示难以置信，他说：“从小到大，你是我在大制作电影中看到的第一批黑人演员之一，所以这让我难以置信”。这位演员回答道：“这对你来说是一个信号，表明系统性种族主义不是你可以轻易应对的事情，”然后补充道：“这种多样性的概念还有很长的路要走。系统性种族主义不会很快改变”。</p><p>这并不是这位明星第一次谈论这个话题。 2023 年，他告诉<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2023/mar/16/i-felt-seriously-cheated-djimon-hounsou-on-the-oscars-poor-pay-days-stardom-and-struggle"><em>《卫报》</em></a> ，“我仍然需要证明为什么我需要得到报酬”，并形容工作室为他的作品开出了“低价”的报价。 ”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/viola-davis">维奥拉·戴维斯</a>说得很漂亮。她赢得了奥斯卡奖、<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/emmys">艾美奖</a>奖、托尼奖，但她仍然拿不到报酬”。</p><p>翰苏继续高产创作，惊悚片<em>《风暴之下》</em>和<em>《狂热者》</em>计划于今年上映。最近，与该演员的<em>《叛逆月亮》</em>搭档索菲亚·宝特拉<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/rebel-moon-star-hits-back-at-critics-who-demolished-the-insanely-derivative-sci-fi-film-3597615">猛烈抨击了那些“毁掉”这部电影的影评人</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/djimon-hounsou-struggling-to-make-a-living-3828340">《血钻》和《角斗士》的主演杰蒙·翰苏 (Djimon Hounsou) 尽管有着辉煌的职业生涯，但“努力谋生”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
